description:
In this video, Adam will be showing you how to personalise your heroes and characters with upgrade kits and custom paint schemes. This video will take you through a step by step process to making your own custom Dark Angels character. It will also show you how to vary a paint scheme to make a leader unit stand out amongst the rest of your army. These tips will be perfect for both Warhammer 40, 000 and Warhammer Age of Sigmar!

Base Paints:
Abaddon Black
Averland Sunset
Khorne Red
Layer Paints:
Ushabti Bone

If you're new to painting, our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials playlist hosts an array of beginner-friendly videos to help you get started.
